# ============================================================
#  .gitignore — Week-02-Sensors-and-calibration (ESP-IDF)
# ============================================================

# --- ESP-IDF build output (ทุก sub-project) ---
**/build/
**/sdkconfig
**/sdkconfig.old
**/sdkconfig.defaults.esp32

# --- CMake generated files ---
**/CMakeFiles/
**/CMakeCache.txt
**/cmake_install.cmake
**/install_manifest.txt

# --- Ninja build system ---
**/.ninja_deps
**/.ninja_log

# --- Binary / firmware artifacts ---
*.bin
*.elf
*.map
*.hex

# --- ESP-IDF component manager ---
**/dependencies.lock
**/managed_components/

# --- Partition table (auto-generated) ---
**/partition_table/

# --- Flash args (auto-generated) ---
**/flash_args
**/flash_project_args

# --- Python / ESP-IDF tools cache ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
venv/
.env/

# --- Logs & temp ---
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak

# --- macOS ---
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

# --- JetBrains / CLion ---
.idea/

# --- Obsidian vault config ---
.obsidian/
